{"tid":792743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】安泰邨女子12層高行人橋墮下　送院不治","createTime":"2018-08-24T18:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T05:00:38.000Z","uid":50162,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5c69c079faa44ffcf2911e8a357d0dea0f58d6cb","tid":792743,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪安泰邨勇泰樓對出連接順安邨的行人天橋，今早(22日)8時32分，一名56歲姓李內地女子，疑由12層高的天橋梯間墮下，倒臥山坡，消防及救護接報趕至，將女子救起，惟已陷入昏迷，口鼻滲血，由救護車送院搶救，惜告死亡，警方調查後相信死因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n據了解事主近日受感情問題困擾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180722124742\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180722124742&h=b10f96eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子被救起時已陷入昏迷。（趙瑞麟攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180722124742\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180722124742&h=e9113fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子由天橋梯間墮下，警方在現場調查。（趙瑞麟攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180722/photo/bkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180722124742\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180722124742&h=68345ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救護車到場將墮樓女子送院。（趙瑞麟攝）<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180722/bkn-20180722083856045-0722_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h